Package edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.logic

Interface Numeric

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<Logical>, Expression, Logical, Serializable, Simplifiable, Typed
All Known Implementing Classes:
Arithmetic, ArithmeticExpansion, Number
public interface Numeric extends Expression
A numeric expression is a logical expression of type number. This interface implements some functionality that all numeric expressions share, but numeric expressions do not need to implement this interface.
Author:
Stephen G. Ware
